{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_01_01",
  "title": "fran 1話 お金を稼ぎたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "今日から、星見プロでお世話になります\n山田・フランツィスカ・夏織です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From today onwards‚ I'll be under the care of Hoshimi Pro.\nI'm Francisca Kaori Yamada.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそよろしくお願いします、山田さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you‚ Yamada-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでは、星見プロさんのグループと\n戦うことになりましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In I-UNITY‚ we battled against\nHoshimi Pro's group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "これからは、同じ事務所のメンバーとして\nよろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But from now on‚ we're members of the same agency.\nLet's work together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ⅢXは、ステージの完成度とビジュアルがウリの）\n（実力派アイドルグループだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（IIIX is known for their polished stage presence and visuals.）\n（They're a talented idol group.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（いろいろあったけど、今日からは同じ事務所の仲間だ）\n（俺もマネージャーとして、なんとか頑張らないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There were some issues‚ but from today‚ we're fellow members of the same agency.）\n（As a manager‚ I have to do my best somehow…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmph.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "この際……と言うか、最初に言っておきますけど\n私達は便宜上、星見プロに籍を置いておくだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this case… or rather‚ I'll say it upfront.\nWe're simply putting ourselves under Hoshimi Pro for convenience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "一応あなたがマネージャーってことになってますけど\n全部、指示に従うつもりはありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're designated as the manager‚\nbut I won't be following your instructions entirely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "あと、それから\n私のこと山田って呼ぶの止めてくれません？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚\nCan you stop calling me Yamada?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え……でも、山田さん……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… but you are Yamada-san‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "似合わないでしょ、私のこの金髪にその名前！\nfranって芸名があるんだから\nそっちにして下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn't it look strange‚ that name with my blonde hair?\nI have the stage name \"fran.\"\nCall me fran instead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（な……何が地雷なのかも、全然分からない）\n（これは、一緒に仕事するにも苦労しそうだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I… I have no idea what's going on.）\n（This is going to be a challenging job…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は、スリクスが移籍して初めてのイベントだ）\n（まあベテランだし、緊張はしてないだろうけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today is IIIX's first event after transferring.）\n（Well‚ they're veterans‚ so I guess they're not nervous…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあああああああああああ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaaaaaaaaaah!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3100.0000000000086,
          "startTime": 93.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.333333300013,
          "startTime": 93.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "franさん！　何があったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san! What happened!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ……昼休みに謝罪会見するってどういうこと！？\nせめて閉場後にしなさいよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait… A press conference during lunch break!?\nAt least do it after closing time!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの午後から株価暴落するに決まってるじゃない！\nああ～もう、あっという間にナイアガラ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's obvious that the stock prices will plummet in the afternoon!\nAh~Nosediving…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふ……ふふ……これでいくらマイナスかしら……\n全部突っ込んでなくて良かったけどさ……けどさ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… I wonder how much of a loss this is…\nIt's a relief that I didn't invest everything‚ but still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "あ？　見たら分かるでしょ、株やってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? You'll understand if you look‚ I'm into stocks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "か……株……？\nああ、今はスマホでも株取引が出来るんでしたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Stocks…?\nAh‚ right. You can do stock trading on smartphones nowadays.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ\nああー……これダメね、少しでも損害減らせるかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly.\nAh… This is bad. I wonder if I can minimize the loss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく最近は黒字だったのに、全部パァ\nああー……もう嫌、今日はやる気なくなったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was finally in the black recently‚ and now it's all gone.\nAh… I'm so fed up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "もう何もしたくない……\n帰って寝たい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't feel like doing anything anymore…\nI just want to go home and sleep…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.3333333333,
